Summit =20

Director Crowe took part in the Women Mean Business Summit on Friday, March=
 20th at MGM National Harbor, joining a panel of influential women leaders =
for a conversation on business growth, leadership, and economic opportunity=
. Hosted by the Women=E2=80=99s Business Enterprise Council (WBEC) Greater =
DMV, the Summit offered an immersive experience filled with high=E2=80=91im=
pact networking, strategic introductions, and opportunities for women to le=
arn from one another and build meaningful partnerships.

Summit 3=20

Her participation carried added importance as the event took place during W=
omen=E2=80=99s History Month, a time dedicated to recognizing women=E2=80=
=99s achievements and expanding opportunities for future generations. By sh=
aring her experience and perspective, Director Crowe contributed to a broad=
er effort to support women=E2=80=99s advancement in business and public ser=
vice.

