OWM) provided guidance on consumer rights, scam prevention, reporting viola=
tions, and the importance of accurate weighing, measuring, and scanning dev=
ices. Shoppers also asked questions, and expressed appreciation for DLCP=E2=
=80=99s presence in their neighborhoods.

