  *=20

More information available at dcra.dc.gov/industrial-trade [ https://dcra.d=
c.gov/industrial-trade ].

Combat Sports License Renewal

Deadline: March 31, 2026


  *=20

Renew online through Access DC [ https://govservices.dcra.dc.gov/oplarenewa=
llicense ] (Sign Up and email verification required).


  *=20

Licensees are encouraged to renew early to avoid additional fees.


  *=20

Licenses not renewed by March 31, 2026 require reinstatement.


  *=20

Reinstatement is allowed for up to five years; after that, applicants must =
reapply as first=E2=80=91time licensees.


  *=20

